SELECT \n    CASE \n        WHEN price BETWEEN 50 AND 100 THEN '$50 - $100'\n        WHEN price BETWEEN 100 AND 500 THEN '$100 - $500'\n        WHEN price BETWEEN 500 AND 1000 THEN '$500 - $1000'\n        ELSE 'Other'\n    END AS PriceRange,\n    COUNT(*) AS ProductCount\nFROM \n    Products\nGROUP BY \n    CASE \n        WHEN price BETWEEN 50 AND 100 THEN '$50 - $100'\n        WHEN price BETWEEN 100 AND 500 THEN '$100 - $500'\n        WHEN price BETWEEN 500 AND 1000 THEN '$500 - $1000'\n        ELSE 'Other'\n    END\nORDER BY\n    MIN(price);